    {
      "id": "36",
      "name": "更多訊息",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "customize",
          "data": {
            "data": {
              "parsed_content": [
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "對話",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 1,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "日常對話",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 2,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "「成為王的人...」",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "馬克利：",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "妳/你也想成為牌手嗎，如果妳/你也想成為牌手的話，就一定要記得，最後成為「七聖召喚」之王的人，一定是我！",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "對話1：",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "那就來試試看吧！",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "馬克利（玩家勝利）：",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "...失敗總是難免的，真是精彩的對局。不過...我是不會因為一次失敗就放棄自己身為牌手的靈魂的！",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "馬克利（玩家失敗）：",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "只要能這樣接連不斷地取得勝利，最後，我一定能夠成為「七聖召喚」的王者吧。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "對話2：",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "喔。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "馬克利：",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "唉，你的反應也太冷淡了點吧...",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "七聖召喚",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 1,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "決鬥對局",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 2,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "關卡介紹",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "發誓從貓尾酒館開始征服整個「七聖召喚」界的傳奇牌手，在貓尾酒館裡四處尋找能配得上自己的對手。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(204, 191, 173)"
                      ],
                      "text": "【提示】這是一位強大的牌手，建議牌手等級高一些再來挑戰。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "對手陣容",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 3198,
                      "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/02/181140897/6c1a40b971633c08f8f376ce5bc61f7c_2775052450655518776.png",
                      "menu_id": 17,
                      "name": "丘丘岩盔王",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 3181,
                      "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/02/292125737/1692ce668a14a238e1fa6b763b9ae0ce_3135311874516896749.png",
                      "menu_id": 17,
                      "name": "迪盧克",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 3187,
                      "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/02/181140897/31f1af14b97e8b36a6617bfa7f094abb_5057158303044200307.png",
                      "menu_id": 17,
                      "name": "雷澤",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "解鎖要求",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "「牌手等級」到達1級",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "獲勝獎勵",
